history.content:
CS70 does not have lab sections and EE16A has different TAs for lab sections and discussion sections so you do not need to match the numbers. Just pick the sections that fit your schedule. 

I'm not sure about CS 61B; when I took it last spring I had different lab and discussion TAs and they never seemed to care, but policies may have changed.

For CS61A we were told that our section number for discussion and lab should match, so that we have the same GSI for these sections. Is this also true for EE16B, CS 61B and CS 70?
